						               													<description>This expansion will send you in search of the pieces of the famous Alembic of Valengarde, which split into 3 upon Ninidazir&amp;rsquo;s death and have been wandering the country ever since.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Whether you search out each piece or come across them by happy accident, you will need to 'transport' them to the same Terrain card. Once they are grouped together, you will be able to open this mysterious little box that contains the - permanently - reconstructed Alembic of Valengarde.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Of course, this will not be an easy task, because saving the game or returning to the Citadel before completing this task will cause the mischievous pieces of Alembic to wander off, forcing you to begin your search anew.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;But you can take our word for it, it's well worth the trouble!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Contents: 30 cards, 4 minis.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
